divs: Sighting DetailsI was talking to my friend and we were sitting on his porch wh we both saw three flashing star-like objects flying side-by-side in the night sky...Then I turned my head for a better few and they sped up very then disapeared....we talked about how weird it was then we both shrugged it off...
Summary: Three star-like flashing objects flying in unison and moving as fast as a jet. Then they sped up and disapeared.
